column5: It’s nice to see ur not to only one going through this. Buts it’s also sad. I used to be sane in the mind. Enough to not be suicidal. Now, I just wanna end it. And the ONLY reason I won’t or didn’t so far is because of my family and friends. So they won’t be fucked up from my decisions. But that’s one of the reasons why I want to move away where nobody knows me. It is what it is . This world has nothing to offer and I have nothing to offer it back anymore .
